settings.editor: Below are some frequently asked questions we often get. Please preview the FAQs to see if any of them answer your specific question.

tabs.tab_title: Q. WHAT DO YOU CHARGE FOR YOUR GRAPHIC DESIGN SERVICES?
tabs.tab_content: Pricing depends on many variables, but you can be sure that you are getting great value for your design project. Design jobs are calculated by the hour.

tabs.tab_title: Q. IS THE ARTWORK OUR PROPERTY ONCE PAID FOR?
tabs.tab_content: No, not actual artwork files unless agreed upon in the presentation.

tabs.tab_title: Q. HOW WILL I RECEIVE MY DESIGN PROJECT ONCE IT IS FINISHED?
tabs.tab_content: Final project to you upon receipt of final payment. Upon your request, we will provide you with a copy of the project files on CD, drop box, or via email. We also keep an original of your project on file for subsequent updates.

tabs.tab_title: Q: How will I pay you and how much money will you take?
